de.mrapp.android.tabswitcher

Class Animation.Builder<AnimationType,BuilderType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.tabswitcher.Animation.Builder<AnimationType,BuilderType>
  • Type Parameters:
    AnimationType - The type of the animations, which are created by the builder
    BuilderType - The type of the builder
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PeekAnimation.Builder, RevealAnimation.Builder, SwipeAnimation.Builder
    Enclosing class:
    Animation

    protected abstract static class Animation.Builder<AnimationType,BuilderType>
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract base class for all builders, which allow to configure and create instances of the class Animation.
